name: Psychedelic multicolored flowers glowing iridescently in the dark
description:
Woods below. The moon rose, full and bright and large, a pale silver light washing over the forest floor. The wind died down to a whisper. The fire in the fire pit died down to a few embers.

After the moon set and the stars began to glow, we started a small fire in the fire pit.

The night was full of songbirds. We heard the soft cooing of love songs and the songs of mourning. The air grew heavier with the weight of a thousand voices all singing at once. We felt love in the air. The air felt charged, full of passion.
